                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box col-lg-4">
                        <img class="feature wow fadeInUp" src="/image/pro-pic.svg">
                        <h2 class="wow animated fadeInUp">分類簡潔</h2>
                        <p class="detail wow animated fadeInUp">攝影/剪輯/文字/其他，一目瞭然，讓人才適得其所</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box col-lg-4">
                        <img class="feature wow fadeInUp" src="/image/pro-pic.svg">
                        <h2 class="wow animated fadeInUp">沒有現金流的參與</h2>
